speech.p: Amendments proposed: Government No. 1, in page 1, line 9, at end insert
', or a judge of the Crown Court nominated for the purposes of this section by the Head of Criminal Justice,'
Government No. 2, in page 1, line 16, at end insert
'or a judge of the Crown Court who shall have been designated by the Lord Chief Justice or by a judge nominated by him to try the case.'. .— [Mr. Mike O'Brien.]
